  "instructions": [
    "Boil 2 cups of water and cook sliced figs for 2 minutes until soft, then drain them;",
    "Heat olive oil in a skillet and toast diced pita bread until golden and crisp;",
    "In a large bowl combine chopped romaine, diced cucumber, sliced red onion, pomegranate seeds, and the softened figs;",
    "Add the toasted pita croutons to the bowl;",
    "Drizzle lemon juice and the remaining olive oil over the salad;",
    "Sprinkle sumac, za'atar, chopped mint, and a pinch of salt over the mixture;",
    "Gently toss all ingredients to coat evenly with the spices and dressing;",
    "Serve immediately, allowing the aromatic flavors to mingle within the salad."
  ],
